Package org.biojavax.bio.phylo.io.phylip

Classes to support the reading and writing of PHYLIP format.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
PHYLIPFileListener Listens to events fired by the PHYLIP parser.
 

Class Summary
PHYLIPFileBuilder Builds a PHYLIP file by listening to events.
PHYLIPFileFormat Reads PHYLIP interleaved alignment files and fires events at a PHYLIPFileListener object.
